In one kilometer of kink, up to 1800 different species could live and breed up to 30 pairs of birds.
However, the kink can only fulfill its ecologically important function if it is maintained accordingly in winter.
Otherwise, he withers to a clear row of trees, which, in addition to biodiversity, also loses the wind protection effect, Ludwichowski said.
According to the Ministry of Agriculture, the kink care may only be operated outside the breeding season from October to March.
